{"tid":1462113,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[入嚟屌鳩我]求吓你哋唔好喺機場主動阻路","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T10:32:50.000Z","uid":81045,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ec65b685c92cfe134c71f9b1bb806000580019f7","tid":1462113,"uid":81045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:01:11.000Z","msg":"地鐵玩過不合作運動阻人返工嘅都知道呢啲動作係幾咁失民心<br />\n<br />\n今次仲要阻旅客返屋企，喺佢哋眼中香港人只會變咗喺唔講埋嘅一群，同原本嘅文宣工作背道而馳<br />\n<br />\n連最和理非嘅地方都破壞埋，我覺得宜家係你哋想同和理非割席<br />\n<br />\n機場太多人而機管局機飛係一回事，你主動阻人飛唔到就係完全入哂所有示威者數"},{"pid":"4573a14762ea121df3ea9035cc22761b55b5c589","tid":1462113,"uid":251580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:02:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場 不阻不衝 唔好令示威者形象受損</span></span>"},{"pid":"74b743a933757b120045603bcd48cb4d39e23ad1","tid":1462113,"uid":81045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3fce6382c4705b4a3a6e192033116f3c6dff5be4","tid":1462113,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:08:28.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n但最好隔日咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&